<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="Aink143-kilavi">
        puṟattu taṅkivanta talaimakaṟkut tōḻi colliyatu</p>    <p xml:lang="en">
          Spoken by the confidante to the hero who came, having stayed elsewhere.
 
 </p>
 </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink143">
<l>ekkar ñāḻaṟ puḷḷimi ḻakaṉṟuṟai</l>
<l>yiṉiya ceyta niṉṟupiṉ</l>
<l>muṉivu ceytaviva ṭaṭameṉ ṟōḷē.</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
  <l>This girl's wide, soft shoulders</l>
  <l>Created pleasantness, standing on the wide ghat </l>
    <l>Where birds chirp in Ñāḻal trees on the dunes. </l>
      <l>Later, they created suffering.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
